I mean I talked to GM at various points of the story's development since I'm the author of Vlad's bio 

{{sticker:vlad-salute}} 

And please, please don't make me analyse this story, I'm too innocent for this.

It is true. Blood Magicks was a guest at Riot Games this summer, and she helped us update Vlad's lore.

In fact, I'm pleased to be able to confirm (since she already has!) that she wrote the new bio, too. A great talent, right here.

